parameters: TEマップイベント呼び出し 地下１Fへ 1
ストーリー　砦潜入

Damn it, these slimes keep coming one after
another...!
Move! Hurry up and let me escape!!

Don't push! Even if you push, the slime is...
Aaargh!!!??

Is this... the slimes blocking the path? I don't
know why, but... I'm grateful! I'll take this
chance to move forward.\n< Serena >

But this corpse... it doesn't seem to be the work
of slimes. It looks like it was destroyed by some
tremendous force...\n< Serena >

Anyway, at this rate, it seems they won't have the
capacity to only deal with me. I'll take this
opportunity to break through the front and run
past.\n< Serena >
